200, 尤其是平價底板或者 cas&nbsp;latency 15/16 以上果 d, 唔少 3200 既頂盡都係行 2933"},{"pid":"d7c3ba4e33f1bf3bc993789ad1ff879bc9173b5d","tid":332153,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>求教 3200大法</blockquote><br />\nUpdate 完bios, OC 個到多左個選項。叫做咩dram frequency try 咁樣，揀返try 3200，佢會幫你自己set啲clocks，重開機就搞掂。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nflare x 基本上換個 xmp 就得, 但其他就未必咁容易穩定上到 3200, 尤其是平價底板或者 cas&amp;nbsp;latency 15/16 以上果 d, <span style=\"color: red;\">唔少 3200 既頂盡都係行 2933</span></blockquote><br />\n苦主揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用緊ASUS 辣殺 prime x370<br />\nRAM係b-die 不過係兩條16GB<br />\nXMP標榜行到 3200 C16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMSI x370 可以support 行3200嘅ram <br />\n係多過我用緊呢塊辣殺版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}